==Sister cities==
Memphis has two [[town twinning|sister cities]], as designated by [http://www.sister-cities.org/ Sister Cities International, Inc. (SCI)]: [[Kanifing]] ([[Gambia]]) and [[Kaolack]] ([[Senegal]]).

